title: Arnold Schwarzenegger Will Leave You SPEECHLESS
itunes:title: Arnold Schwarzenegger Will Leave You SPEECHLESS
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
Arnold Schwarzenegger, former Mr. Olympia, Conan, Terminator, and Governor of California, delivers one of the best motivational speeches you will ever hear.


Special thanks to Jürgen Höller for partnering with us in the creation of this video! Subscribe to his channel for the full speech and more like it: https://bit.ly/JürgenHöllerYouTube


Music by Whitesand (https://www.youtube.com/c/WhitesandComposer), and Audiojungle (https://audiojungle.net/).
